fit <- read_csv(paste0(work_dir, "nparact_7days_fit.csv"))
## Parsed with column specification:
## cols(
##   IS = col_double(),
##   IV = col_double(),
##   RA = col_double(),
##   L5 = col_double(),
##   L5_starttime = col_time(format = ""),
##   M10 = col_double(),
##   M10_starttime = col_time(format = ""),
##   record_id = col_double()
## )
fit$Device <- "Fitbit Charge 2 HR"
act <- read_csv(paste0(work_dir, "nparact_7days_act.csv"))
## Parsed with column specification:
## cols(
##   IS = col_double(),
##   IV = col_double(),
##   RA = col_double(),
##   L5 = col_double(),
##   L5_starttime = col_time(format = ""),
##   M10 = col_double(),
##   M10_starttime = col_time(format = ""),
##   record_id = col_double()
## )
act$Device <- "Actiwatch 2.0"

d <- rbind(fit, act)

d$Device <- as.factor(d$Device)
d$Group <- factor(ifelse(d$record_id < 20000, -1, 1), labels = c("Young Adults", "Older Adults"))

d %>%
  group_by(Group, Device) %>%
  summarise_all(list(mean = mean, sd = sd))
## # A tibble: 4 x 18
## # Groups:   Group [2]
##   Group Device IS_mean IV_mean RA_mean L5_mean L5_starttime_me M10_mean
##   <fct> <fct>    <dbl>   <dbl>   <dbl>   <dbl> <drtn>              <dbl>
## 1 Youn Actiw   0.469   0.863   0.876  23.2   12500 secs          354. 
## 2 Youn Fitbi  NA      NA      NA       0.195 15072 secs           12.8
## 3 Olde Actiw   0.528   0.794   0.89   14.8   35508 secs          287. 
## 4 Olde Fitbi   0.394   1.05    0.956   0.16  36888 secs           11.6
## #  with 10 more variables: M10_starttime_mean <drtn>, record_id_mean <dbl>,
## #   IS_sd <dbl>, IV_sd <dbl>, RA_sd <dbl>, L5_sd <dbl>, L5_starttime_sd <dbl>,
## #   M10_sd <dbl>, M10_starttime_sd <dbl>, record_id_sd <dbl>
d %>%
  ggplot() + 
  geom_col(aes(x = Device, y = IS, group = Group, fill = Group)) + 
  theme_classic() + 
  facet_wrap(. ~ Group) + 
  scale_fill_brewer(palette="Set1") 
## Warning: Removed 1 rows containing missing values (position_stack).

d %>%
  ggplot() + 
  geom_col(aes(x = Device, y = IV, group = Group, fill = Group)) + 
  theme_classic() + 
  facet_wrap(. ~ Group) + 
  scale_fill_brewer(palette="Set1") 
## Warning: Removed 1 rows containing missing values (position_stack).

d %>%
  ggplot() + 
  geom_col(aes(x = Device, y = RA, group = Group, fill = Group)) + 
  theme_classic() + 
  facet_wrap(. ~ Group) + 
  scale_fill_brewer(palette="Set1") 
## Warning: Removed 1 rows containing missing values (position_stack).

d %>%
  ggplot() + 
  geom_col(aes(x = Device, y = L5, group = Group, fill = Group)) + 
  theme_classic() + 
  facet_wrap(. ~ Group) + 
  scale_fill_brewer(palette="Set1") 

d %>%
  ggplot() + 
  geom_col(aes(x = Device, y = M10, group = Group, fill = Group)) + 
  theme_classic() + 
  facet_wrap(. ~ Group) + 
  scale_fill_brewer(palette="Set1")
